snippet.title: L'oreal Infallible *FRESH WEAR* Foundation | FULL DAY Wear Test | BeautiCo.
snippet.description:
Be sure to subscribe to my channel and hit the notification bell to get notified when I upload a new video: https://www.youtube.com/beautico

Hey Guys I actually found a gem! This foundation is so good for everyday wear and lasts on my oily skin for soo long and looks super flawless and smooth. A must try!
It has a natural finish to it and does not look heavy at all!

♥️
L'Oreal Paris Infallible 24H Fresh Wear Foundation -300 Amber

L'Oreal Paris Infallible Pro Matte Liquid Lipstick - 358 Cowboy
https://nyk0.page.link/nuFE
♥️
